newsitem.title: EGYPT: Egypt pound overnight, one-week rates narrow.
newsitem.headline: Egypt pound overnight, one-week rates narrow.

text.p: Overnight interbank rates on the Egyptian pound narrowed on Tuesday to 10 1/4 percent in a liquid private sector market from Monday's range of 10 1/4 and 10 3/8 percent, bankers said.
One-week lending rates also narrowed to 10 3/8 percent from 10 3/8 and 10 7/16 percent while public sector banks maintained their minimum overnight lending rate at 10 1/2 percent.
